OL,3,CFamily with autistic child 'drowning'
OL,4,Cover lack of support
OL,6,FChantelle told ITV News: "It's
OL,7,Fdevastating to see her in such a
OL,8,Fconstant state of disregulation -
OL,9,Fshe's constantly angry, and she
OL,10,Fdoesn't know why, which leaves her
OL,11,Fupset. We can't settle her.
OL,13,F"We are drowning because we cannot
OL,14,Fspend any time together.
OL,16,F"We've been crying out for support for
OL,17,Fover a year, and just nothing's
OL,18,Fforthcoming."
