OL,4,Cover lack of support
OL,6,FAlana's parents have even been advised
OL,7,Fseveral times to consider giving up
OL,8,Ftheir daughter to foster care, which
OL,9,Fthey say "is just not an option".
OL,11,FChantelle adds: "We've been told
OL,12,Frepeatedly that we've been offered
OL,13,Feverything they can do, and we do not
OL,14,Fhave any more options left other than
OL,15,Fpositive behaviour service, functional
OL,16,Ffamily therapy, and occupational
OL,17,Ftherapy."
