OL,6,FShe continues that these are all
OL,7,Foptions that the family has tried, but
OL,8,Fhaven't proved effective due to
OL,9,FAlana's complex needs.
OL,11,FAlana attends school but often ends
OL,12,Fthe day feeling "stressed" and
OL,13,F"dysregulated" due to masking her
OL,14,Fcondition, explains Chantelle.
OL,16,FAlana has not been accepted into any
OL,17,Fspecial needs schools in the
OL,18,FBailiwick, despite her diagnosis.
