OL,4,Cover lack of support
OL,6,FAlana's parents are open to medication-
OL,7,Fbased treatment, but in line with
OL,8,Fnational guidelines, this is rarely
OL,9,Foffered to patients with ADHD under
OL,10,Fthe age of six.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Guernsey's mental health
OL,13,Ffacility for children does not take
OL,14,Freferrals based on behaviour unless at
OL,15,Fleast two mental health issues are
OL,16,Fpresent.
OL,18,FIn addition, a social care team said
OL,19,Fthat there were no alternative crisis
OL,20,Finterventions available for children
OL,21,Fof Alana's age.
