OL,6,FThe States had nothing further to add
OL,7,Fabout Alana's case or her parents'
OL,8,Fconcerns.
OL,10,FChantelle told ITV News: "We need a
OL,11,Fmulti-disciplinary and less
OL,12,Ftherapeutic intervention, with more
OL,13,Fmedical support.
OL,15,F"Neurodevelopmental (conditions) are a
OL,16,Fdisability. It affects her entire life
OL,17,Fand ours.
